name: Emo Buddha
description: This NFT is the 1st in the ‘Millennial Buddhas’ collection.  I will be minting Buddha from many sub-cultures and welcome suggestions/requests from collectors. The first five collectors of Emo Buddha will receive a free separate NFT gif of the Emo mandala to meditate upon. After five Emo Buddha are sold I shall set a price for the remaining five mandala gifs. Look out for future Millennial Buddha mints to collect a full set.
